OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA dry morning with long spells
OL,6,Fof sunshine, especially near western
OL,7,Fcoasts. Turning cloudy in the
OL,8,Fafternoon with the odd shower possible
OL,9,Fin the east, staying dry towards the
OL,10,Fcoast.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FHigh
OL,13,Fpressure dominates bringing a dry and
OL,14,Fsettled few days with light winds.
OL,15,FPlenty of bright and sunny spells,
OL,16,Fespecially in the west with the east
OL,17,Fcloudier at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
